* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/ˈkæn.dɪdət/}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˈkæn.dɪ.deɪt/|/ˈkæn.dɪ.dɪt/}}
* {{a|US|colloquially}} {{IPA|/ˈkæn.ɪ.dɪt/|/ˈkæn.ɪ.deɪt/}}<ref name="dialect">[http://www4.uwm.edu/FLL/linguistics/dialect/staticmaps/q_32.html The Dialect Survey]</ref><!--which shows that this is not confined to any region-->
* {{audio|En-us-candidate.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[person]] who is [[run]]ning in an [[election]] or who is [[apply]]ing to a [[position]] for a [[job]].
